action.description: Passed Third Reading as amended in HD 2 with Representative(s) Hussey, Olds, Reyes Oda voting aye with reservations; Representative(s) Alcos, Garcia, Kila, Kong, Lamosao, Matsumoto, Muraoka, Pierick, Shimizu voting no (9) and Representative(s) Cochran excused (1).  Transmitted to Senate.
